steps.description:
Analyze a query plan:
```sql
EXPLAIN SELECT count() FROM system.numbers WHERE number > 100;

EXPLAIN actions=1 SELECT count() FROM system.numbers WHERE number > 100;

EXPLAIN PIPELINE SELECT count() FROM system.numbers WHERE number > 100;

EXPLAIN SYNTAX SELECT * FROM system.numbers WHERE number = 1 OR number = 2;
```

EXPLAIN PLAN settings: `header` (0/1), `description` (0/1), `actions` (0/1).
